headline: Post Acute Analytics Closes New Round of Financing to Drive Innovation in Post-Acute Care
summary: DALLAS, September 15, 2025--Post Acute Analytics ("PAA"), the industry leader in intelligent care transition solutions, today announced the successful close of its latest funding round. The financing included participation from Humana and one other strategic investor, as well as existing investors, including Warburg Pincus, Dorilton Capital, and Generator Ventures.
